## Test data generation

A dosage test fixture is needed for phases 1‚Äì3. Generate from a VCF with
dosage annotations:

```bash
# Create a small VCF with DS field (4 samples √ó 4 variants)
# Then convert:
plink2 --vcf test/data/dosage_example.vcf dosage=DS \
       --make-pgen --out test/data/dosage_example
```

The VCF should include:
- Variants with non-integer dosages (e.g., 0.5, 1.3, 1.98)
- At least one variant with missing dosage
- At least one variant with all-hardcall (no dosage track)

This fixture is shared across all phases. Phase 1 can start with hardcall-only
data for plumbing validation, then add the dosage fixture.

