## Suggested ordering

**Phase 1 ‚Üí Phase 2 ‚Üí Phase 3**

Phase 1 establishes the core pattern (PgrGetD + Dosage16ToDoublesMinus9) in
the main scan paths. Phase 2 extends to all mode combinations ‚Äî mostly
mechanical given the element-type abstraction. Phase 3 is independent of
phases 1‚Äì2 (different function, different pgenlib API) but benefits from
the shared dosage test fixture.

### Estimated scope

- Phase 1: ~150 lines new/modified code, ~100 lines tests
- Phase 2: ~200 lines new/modified code, ~150 lines tests
- Phase 3: ~100 lines new/modified code, ~80 lines tests
